,"time_end":85.44},{"position":32,"content":"Sometimes the sky is red at night or in the morning.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/94-favorite-colors-2019-04-07-03-51-10/32.mp3","time_start":85.97,"time_end":89.52},{"position":33,"content":"Artists use all these colors to make beautiful paintings.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/94-favorite-colors-2019-04-07-03-51-10/33.mp3","time_start":90.34,"time_end":94.22},{"position":34,"content":"Nature used all these colors to make the beautiful earth.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/94-favorite-colors-2019-04-07-03-51-10/34.mp3","time_start":94.44,"time_end":97.8},{"position":35,"content":"We are fortunate to be surrounded by beauty.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/94-favorite-colors-2019-04-07-03-51-10/35.mp3","time_start":98.25,"time_end":100.94},{"position":36,"content":"We should do our part to make sure that nature stays beautiful and clean.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/94-favorite-colors-2019-04-07-03-51-10/36.mp3","time_start":101.31,"time_end":106.28}]}